  npcName: Effigy of Nick Ashley
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 615326300704808915, guid: 5816702c1f4306546b8c5db10043762d,
    type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - We're no strangers at all... You know the greeting, and so do I!
  - Being inviting's what I'm thinking of. But I'm more formal than any other guy~
  - I just want to give you a nice greeting... acknowledge, show I- understand!
  - Never gonna say "what's up?", never gonna start with a frown, never gonna run
    around and not greet you
  - Never gonna blink my eyes, never gonna do a high-five, just gonna shake the hand
    and ask, "How d'you do?"
